{"tid":710323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(厲害了我的國系列)三和大神之前NHK已經拍紀錄片講大陸農民工啲小朋友點讀書","createTime":"2018-06-20T16:00:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T10:00:04.000Z","uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eab87a1263ef6de353f4b88aea8dc3ba174c73a7","tid":710323,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T16:00:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VLJyQCn_Mf8&amp;t=3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVLJyQCn_Mf8%26t%3D3s&d=En0ltqR17WZl%2Bf5Y1kYouqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=ad9a0f12\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VLJyQCn_Mf8&amp;t=3s</a><br />\n戶籍制度幾麻煩大家都應該知<br />\n冇戶籍又冇錢既小朋友想讀書幾咁慘<br />\n鄭州已經係上緊黎既一線城市<br />\n大家可以睇下呢D城市點樣排斥外省人(農民工都係外省多)<br />\n又可以睇下啲家長幾懶懶閒<br />\n個妹妹仔老母明知個女冇書讀都唔去交文件<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e58bf67c35bf594939528a1e64ab19fcb4ba57","tid":710323,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T16:02:04.000Z","msg":"五毛賈雨村抹黑本土派有功<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/132845_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F132845_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=211da708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/132849_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F132849_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=1ad97502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/132859_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F132859_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=bbe0f1ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來大陸仔嚟<img src=\"/as